➜凭什么牛配B是夸人，狗配B就成了骂人？怎么想都是你们人类的错
http://www.sohu.com/a/425057591_624188	14962
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201016/38ee226a19824993b81e7691a6e891e2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">26个英文字母里面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最特别的一个无疑就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201016/d92940da715b40d19bade88994022682.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201016/697dc03db8a2430ba9ea64920e18c9a2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">就比如最常见的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“牛B”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“狗B”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201016/96d2d40e49ae43cb911a4093ff63f8dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就让人很疑惑了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">明明大家都是哺乳动物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都是人类的好朋友</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就只是后面加了个<strong>“B”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>凭什么牛配B是夸人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>狗配B就成了骂人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这究竟是什么不同导致的结果？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201016/4563b954f5cc4180ab971d17fd0c37a6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">首先要明确的一点是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夸人和骂人的锅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不该B来背</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟说<strong>“你太牛了”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和<strong>“你太狗了”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也都表示差不多的意思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201016/5e2d871c797948a6b26b5c85f75da123.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">少了B就缺了点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>内味儿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这主要原因是B是个<strong>闭塞音</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发音时气流通路完全闭塞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放在词尾发出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就让人感觉很舒爽很解气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还增添了几分<strong>氛围加强效果</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让牛的更牛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">狗的更狗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就仅此而已没有更多了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以这一切根源</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是得<strong>从牛和狗自身上找原因</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201016/3a73907161924f498794c9765ffbe14f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>狗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为人类最早驯化的动物之一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">具有<strong>极高的服从性</strong>且<strong>忠诚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样的形容</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从表面上并不是贬义的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201016/89fa25f10d734d169ef413f4c212e16d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你们也知道的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就是容易膨胀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你太乖了他反而在潜意识里觉得</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你这是奴性的表现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是一种下对上的跪舔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就让狗天然有了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>低人一等</strong>的感觉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201016/d807bf961f7f4219b35e2e6fb35d54af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再加之狗受人使唤后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还喜滋滋摇尾巴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱舔人的友好样子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让本就非常膨胀的人类感觉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>谄媚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是便有了<strong>狗腿子、狗奴才</strong>的说法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">按照现代话来说这就都是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>舔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>狗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201016/474a6dabcefb46f5b80e3857746246eb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在这一切的前面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有更重要的一点是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是那句恒久流传的经典名言</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
狗改不了吃屎
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱吃屎的动物不止狗一种</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但总爱在人类面前吃屎的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">狗算是<strong>一枝独秀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就让本来地位不高的狗子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身价一跌再跌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201016/1e98ffa3aa04464e9277848fee1d322b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>《资治通鉴》</strong>里就有骂人名言</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
啖狗屎高丽奴！
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">这意思就不用朕多解释了吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">懂的都懂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201016/ad776c374d054b239d2c504461aaf74b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除此之外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>光明正大的交配</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也成了狗被诟病的原因之一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">理由和吃屎一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不关上门交配的动物千千万</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总爱在人类眼皮子底下就交配的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">狗又是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一枝独秀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟在大街上就有不少</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至你的腿都可能曾为此献身</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201016/47fd5bcf43704ae6ab740707359a3dab.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为含蓄内敛的中国人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说出“交配”二字都<strong>羞耻万分</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">常用为爱鼓掌/啪啪啪等词来代替</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而狗却干的如此光明正大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更让人感觉到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不耻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就导致</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当你搜索与狗有关的成语时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>基本没什么好词</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201016/eb2f4740a37c4371884af62f01c0c349.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而更卑微的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">狗不仅是古代骂人专用词</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至成了<strong>诅咒人的道具</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据记载</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>郑庄公</strong>的恩人<strong>颖考叔</strong>被暗箭射杀后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">郑庄公搞了个<strong>诅咒守灵仪式</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来诅咒那个射杀颖考叔的扑街</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这诅咒中就用到了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>狗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>被诅咒的人正好是守灵人之一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天天听自己被诅咒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后受不了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大喊一声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“人是我杀的”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抹脖子死人了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201016/54379ff4caef4b178cddd5a46e4684d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
郑伯使卒出豭，行出犬鸡，以诅射颖考叔者——《左传》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">对比起卑微的狗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>牛的身份地位就高很多了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201016/1cc6129b7ecc4f0e838a11311a2403b9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中国古代以<strong>农耕</strong>为主</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在工业不发达的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛可以说是<strong>相当重要的物资</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟牛不仅有利于耕作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平时拉货也用得上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">死了还能做成各种战争物资</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以说<strong>比人都有用多了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《宋刑统》</strong>中就有规定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>私自杀牛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一年起刑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201016/1b2024cecdcc451d86d2a6dbe031e6e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
诸故杀官私牛者，徒一年半。主自杀牛马者徒一年。——《宋刑统》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有<strong>皇帝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才能在<strong>春秋</strong>两个季节</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宰牛羊豕来祭天祭祖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">称之为“太牢”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而<strong>诸侯</strong>祭祀则用的是“少牢”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相比太牢里面就少了牛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">轮到<strong>大夫</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就只能用一种动物祭祀了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而那一种<strong>肯定不会是牛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由此足以见证</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那是真的牛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201016/0cbe3941019d49efa0eee992da8694cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从社会地位上看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛已经<strong>全面碾压了狗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而和狗改不了吃屎一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛也有着自己的专属经典名言</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——<strong>吹牛皮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只不过吹牛皮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更凸显了牛的<strong>牛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201016/629f914fb4f04ed38cf29ae72b13b380.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201016/f12260ba8c4646979db75862236a7800.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">关于吹牛皮有两种说法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在没桥没船的年代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们为了过河</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就<strong>用牛皮做成筏子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于为什么不选马皮驴皮呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那还是归功于<strong>牛皮结实又耐操</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201016/221ee97f03824f4581de0a22ce9527c1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太结实耐操也带来了新的问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>难</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在没有打气筒的年代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全程只能靠<strong>嘴</strong>来吹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就导致吹一个牛皮筏子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">得要<strong>几个彪形大汉轮流吹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是有人说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">靠自己一个人就可以吹牛皮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那明显就是<strong>说大话</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201016/32fddd82ce064a1d97bb82bfe96eacba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以前杀猪宰羊时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会在它们割开一个小口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后插<strong>管</strong>往里吹气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把它们身体吹膨胀起来后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刮毛剥皮就很方便</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201016/e86ed62bdfc4411ebd49c65b73360e5c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吹牛就很难了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛皮非常坚韧，皮下脂肪少</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本身还很大只</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个人插根管就想把牛给吹起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那明显也是不行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201016/6ee8e46980ba40faba1664407e575790.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由此均可证明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吹牛皮=说大话</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而“<strong>吹</strong>”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">单独拿出来也可以有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>说大话</strong>的意味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“你就吹吧”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“你吹上天我都不会信的”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201016/851f335e66e2430989fb9a49bc185e44.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛皮的存在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实是<strong>加强了吹的程度</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加上了牛皮的吹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相当于</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吹得也太过了/吹得太厉害了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以四舍五入我们可以得到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>牛皮=太过了、太厉害了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201016/d26f1b3ffe9f413ea038d1cdab78f909.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而“<strong>皮”</strong>字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在一些方言里面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有着哔——的含义</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从读法上来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">B和P读起来差别倒也不是特别大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛B这不就产生了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201016/d28cf9f8161b48e7bd73dc86670ec641.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了以上理由外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛B很牛还有一点重要的原因就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">母牛的这个部位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是普通人能见到最大的了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以这真的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>很牛B</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201016/85cacb08e35b498ca05a7e94a5006144.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本文系【朕说】原创内容</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">未经账号授权，禁止随意转载</p>